description: The adviser employs two different investment strategies depending on whether the index anticipates a bull market or a bear market. At least 80% of the fund's total assets will be invested in the component securities of the index. The index seeks to determine whether U.S. equity markets appear to be a "Bull" indicator or appear to have a "Bear" indicator. The fund is non-diversified.
name: Alpha Architect Merlyn.AI Best-of-Breed Core Momentum ETF
